{"schemaVersion":1,"bookId":"toefl-sentences","unitId":"sentence-029","title":"Sentence 29","sectionId":"sentences-021","sectionTitle":"Sentence 21-30","pageStart":200,"pageEnd":205,"extractionMethod":"text-layer","wordEntryCount":23,"duplicateEntryCount":2,"pages":[{"number":200,"blocks":[{"type":"title","text":"Sentence 29"},{"type":"text","text":"When Henry Ford first sought financial backing for making cars, the"},{"type":"text","text":"very notion of farmers and clerks owning automobiles was considered"},{"type":"text","text":"ridiculous."},{"type":"text","text":"当亨利·福特最初为制造汽车寻求资金支持时，人们觉得“农民和"},{"type":"text","text":"一般职员都能拥有汽车”这种想法太可笑了。"},{"type":"section","text":"语法笔记"},{"type":"text","text":"本句的主干是The notion was considered ridiculous。句中when引导"},{"type":"text","text":"时间状语从句；现在分词短语owning automobiles作后置定语修饰"},{"type":"text","text":"farmers and clerks。"},{"type":"section","text":"核心词表"},{"type":"entry","text":"seek /siːk/ v. 寻找；寻求","headword":"seek"},{"type":"note","text":"记忆 一直想找到（seek）一辆线条流畅的（sleek）小汽车"},{"type":"note","text":"搭配 seek for 寻找"},{"type":"text","text":"seek sth. out 挑选出"},{"type":"note","text":"同根 seeker n. 寻找者；追求者"},{"type":"entry","text":"financial /faɪˈnænʃl/ a. 财政的；财务的；金融的","headword":"financial"},{"type":"note","text":"记忆 来自finance（n. 金融；财政）"},{"type":"note","text":"搭配 financial deficit 财政赤字"},{"type":"text","text":"financial aid 经济援助"}]},{"number":201,"blocks":[{"type":"note","text":"同根 finance n. 财政，金融"},{"type":"text","text":"financier n. 金融家"},{"type":"text","text":"financially ad. 财政上，金融上"},{"type":"entry","text":"notion /ˈnoʊʃn/ n. 观念；信念；理解","headword":"notion"},{"type":"note","text":"记忆 not（知道）+ion（名词后缀）→知道→有了概念和想法→概"},{"type":"text","text":"念；想法"},{"type":"note","text":"同根 notional a. 理论上的"},{"type":"text","text":"notionally ad. 理论上"},{"type":"entry","text":"consider /kənˈsɪdər/ v. 考虑，思考；认为；体谅","headword":"consider"},{"type":"note","text":"搭配 all things considered 总而言之"},{"type":"note","text":"同根 consideration n. 考虑，思考；体谅"},{"type":